### Project Specific: NYC Taxi ###
# Ignore large downloaded data files but keep the directory structure
# This includes specific patterns requested for the importer
/backend/importer/data/*.gz
/backend/importer/data/*.dat
/backend/importer/data/*.sql
/backend/importer/data/*.dump
data/*.gz
data/*.dat

